		"Reversi
	]em
	" is a strategic board game that, with its checkered board and simple pieces, may look similar to games like Go or Checkered, but actually plays very differently. Two players take turns placing their colored pieces on a board. Any piece that lies on a straight line and is surrounded by the opponent's pieces gets turned into one of the opponent's pieces. Once all playable squares are filled, the person with the most pieces on the board wins the game.
